  Sample request / response JSON

  POST /api/v1/appointments
  {
    "doctorId": "DOC-1042",
    "patientId": "PAT-8821",
    "specialty": "cardiology",
    "appointmentDate": "2026-07-10",
    "timeSlot": "10:30",
    "appointmentType": "consultation",
    "symptoms": ["chest pain","fatigue"],
    "insuranceId": "ICICI-HLT-90213"
